<br>
1) FD<br>
2) target a corpse<br>
3) /corpse it<br>
<br>
Do this until every corpse you can reach is in a pile where you are. Then:<br>
<br>
4) move and FD.<br>
5) target corpse in previous pile<br>
6) /corpse it<br>
<br>
This way you can drag a lot of people at once, without having to get up and run around, and FD again, for each corpse.  It makes CRs go much faster.<br>
<br>
